{"tid":970545,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"演QUEEN傳記片撻着 雷米馬利克認戀Lucy Boynton","createTime":"2019-01-06T02:13:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-06T02:13:37.000Z","uid":41343,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"87e13c8f83d62e90713710abef57f026ec4cb1ba","tid":970545,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T02:13:37.000Z","msg":"美國男星雷米馬利克（Rami Malek）憑精湛演技威盡影視界，繼主演劇集《黑客軍團》（Mr. Robot）為佢贏得艾美獎視帝後，雷米在電影《波希米亞狂想曲：搖滾傳說》（Bohemian Rhapsody）中亦演活傳奇樂隊QUEEN已故主音Freddie Mercury，在剛舉行嘅棕櫚泉國際電影節上，雷米獲得突破表現獎，更撻着片中女星Lucy Boynton，於台上公開戀情。<br />\n<br />\n雷米於2017年拍攝《波希米亞狂想曲：搖滾傳說》時已跟Lucy Boynton傳出緋聞，女方在片中飾演Freddie出櫃前女友Mary Austen，雷米就在棕櫚泉國際電影節頒獎台上大方認愛：「謝謝你，Lucy Boynton，你是我的盟友，我的知己，我的愛人，非常感謝你！」贏得現場熱烈掌聲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190105/large/1546680698_b0dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190105%2Flarge%2F1546680698_b0dd.jpg&h=4f7b9c3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190105/large/1546680696_5ac7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190105%2Flarge%2F1546680696_5ac7.jpg&h=0d062cb1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}